<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.4">
<l>tōyttataṇṭayir veṇṇeypāluṭa ṉuṇṭalumuṭaṉ ṟāyccikaṇ</l>
<l>ṭārttatōḷuṭai yempirāṉeṉṉa raṅkaṉukkaṭi yārkaḷāy</l>
<l>nāttaḻumpeḻa nāraṇāveṉ ṟaḻaittumeytaḻum pattoḻu</l>
<l>tēttiyiṉpuṟun toṇṭarcēvaṭi yēttivāḻttumeṉ ṉeñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart will applaud [by] praising the red feet of the devotees who,</l>
<l>being the servants of</l>
<l rend="indent">our Lord with arms that the cowherdess tied, being enraged at seeing</l>
<l rend="indent">[Him] eat fresh, curdled curds, butter together with milk,</l>
<l rend="indent">my Raṅga,</l>
<l>experience joy calling out, ‘Nārāyaṇa!’ so that [their] tongues become scarred,</l>
<l>prostrate, so that [their] bodies are bruised, [and] extol [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
